snippet.title: I'd KILL YOU as a Worm - Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
play the demo here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3351470/Id_KILL_YOU_as_a_Worm/

In this wormy game you play as a worm and have to navigate the world in order to find and "take out" your boyfriend.

you turned into a worm.
your boyfriend left you.
you have to kill him.

this game is like getting over it, pogostuck or jump king. it's easy to learn and difficult to master. Throughout the game challenges will be thrown at you that only a true worm would be able to wriggle themselves through. do you have what it takes?

#wormingoverit #gaming #godot #indiedev
